%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!49 &-6132368526687919061
TextAsset:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_Name: EmbeddedYaml
  m_Script: "Conversation1:\r\n- CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_04d64b899837\r\n 
    LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Jared... we\u2019re definitely off-trail.\r\n   
    fr: Jared... on s'est clairement \xE9gar\xE9s.\r\n    es: Jared... definitivamente
    nos perdimos del sendero.\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n  LineID: L_cb8d04d73eed\r\n 
    LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Technically, we\u2019re *still* in the forest.
    Nature counts.\r\n    fr: Techniquement, on est toujours dans la for\xEAt. \xC7a
    compte, non?\r\n    es: T\xE9cnicamente, seguimos en el bosque. Eso cuenta.\r\n-
    CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_8205ac8c4e8a\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en:
    We\u2019ve circled that tree three times now.\r\n    fr: On a tourn\xE9 autour
    de cet arbre trois fois.\r\n    es: Hemos rodeado ese \xE1rbol tres veces.\r\n-
    CharacterID: Jared\r\n  LineID: L_9cd861a48566\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n   
    en: It\u2019s a popular tree. Five stars on TreeAdvisor.\r\n    fr: C\u2019est
    un arbre populaire. Cinq \xE9toiles sur TreeAdvisor.\r\n    es: Es un \xE1rbol
    famoso. Cinco estrellas en TreeAdvisor.\r\n- CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_e01c38d35e8f\r\n 
    LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Shh! Did you hear that?\r\n    fr: Chut! T\u2019as
    entendu \xE7a ?\r\n    es: \xA1Shh! \xBFEscuchaste eso?\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n 
    LineID: L_8e7776524b04\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Maybe it\u2019s a bear.
    Or a ranger with snacks.\r\n    fr: Peut-\xEAtre un ours. Ou un garde forestier
    avec des snacks.\r\n    es: Quiz\xE1s un oso. O un guardabosques con bocadillos.\r\n-
    CharacterID: Wolfstag\r\n  LineID: L_ec0dec9027e2\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n   
    en: *A towering silhouette appears between the trees. Antlers like twisted branches.*\r\n   
    fr: *Une silhouette massive \xE9merge entre les arbres. Des bois torsad\xE9s.*\r\n   
    es: *Una silueta imponente aparece entre los \xE1rboles. Astas retorcidas.*\r\n-
    CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_603c3f4ba4d6\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en:
    What is *that?!*\r\n    fr: C\u2019est quoi *\xE7a* ?!\r\n    es: \xBF\xA1Qu\xE9
    es *eso*!?\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n  LineID: L_d1cfb2aa2db7\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n   
    en: *gasps* Whoooooa. Look at you!\r\n    fr: *hal\xE8tement* Wooooow. Regarde-moi
    \xE7a!\r\n    es: *jadea* \xA1Wooooow! \xA1M\xEDrate!\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n 
    LineID: L_16a17b3396e4\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Are you lost too, buddy?
    You need scritches? Huh? Who\u2019s a majestic forest beast? *You* are!\r\n   
    fr: Tu t\u2019es perdu aussi, mon grand ? Tu veux des gratouilles ? Qui est une
    b\xEAte majestueuse ? *C\u2019est toi!*\r\n    es: \xBFTambi\xE9n est\xE1s perdido,
    amigo? \xBFQuieres caricias? \xBFQui\xE9n es una bestia majestuosa? \xA1*T\xFA*!\r\n-
    CharacterID: Wolfstag\r\n  LineID: L_fecc5a327214\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n   
    en: *It tilts its head slightly. Curious.*\r\n    fr: *Il incline l\xE9g\xE8rement
    la t\xEAte. Curieux.*\r\n    es: *Inclina ligeramente la cabeza. Curioso.*\r\n-
    CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_4e12510204f1\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en:
    Jared\u2026 stop trying to pet the antler demon!\r\n    fr: Jared\u2026 arr\xEAte
    d\u2019essayer de caresser le d\xE9mon \xE0 bois!\r\n    es: \xA1Jared... deja
    de intentar acariciar al demonio de los cuernos!\r\n- CharacterID: Wolfstag\r\n 
    LineID: L_81d918d79d10\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: *The shadows melt away.
    The creature\u2019s full form is revealed\u2014fur glows silver in the moonlight.*\r\n   
    fr: *Les ombres se dissipent. La cr\xE9ature se d\xE9voile \u2014 sa fourrure
    luit \xE0 la lumi\xE8re lunaire.*\r\n    es: *Las sombras se desvanecen. Su forma
    completa aparece \u2014 su pelaje brilla bajo la luna.*\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n 
    LineID: L_44b11d6cd642\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Oh my god. He\u2019s
    gorgeous. I want ten of him.\r\n    fr: Oh mon dieu. Il est splendide. J\u2019en
    veux dix.\r\n    es: Dios m\xEDo. Es hermoso. Quiero diez.\r\n- CharacterID:
    Ava\r\n  LineID: L_b06da097d428\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: ...I think
    he\u2019s leading us somewhere.\r\n    fr: ...Je crois qu\u2019il nous guide
    quelque part.\r\n    es: ...Creo que nos est\xE1 guiando.\r\n- CharacterID: Wolfstag\r\n 
    LineID: L_9379a5301f7e\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: *He glances back, takes
    a few careful steps, then waits.*\r\n    fr: *Il jette un regard en arri\xE8re,
    avance lentement, puis s\u2019arr\xEAte.*\r\n    es: *Mira hacia atr\xE1s, da
    unos pasos y espera.*\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n  LineID: L_b5e5b1e08f68\r\n 
    LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Look at him! He\u2019s so polite. Trail angel confirmed.\r\n   
    fr: Regarde-le ! Trop poli. Ange du sentier confirm\xE9.\r\n    es: \xA1M\xEDralo!
    Tan educado. \xC1ngel del sendero confirmado.\r\n- CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID:
    L_6c2df39ca769\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: I think he wants us to follow.
    And... I think we should.\r\n    fr: Il veut qu\u2019on le suive. Et... je crois
    qu\u2019on devrait.\r\n    es: Quiere que lo sigamos. Y... creo que debemos hacerlo.\r\n-
    CharacterID: Wolfstag\r\n  LineID: L_ff77ae8df82b\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n   
    en: *The creature moves ahead again, parting the brush. Bits of a path peek through
    behind him.*\r\n    fr: *La cr\xE9ature avance \xE0 nouveau, \xE9cartant les
    buissons. Un sentier appara\xEEt derri\xE8re lui.*\r\n    es: *La criatura avanza,
    apartando los arbustos. Se revela un sendero detr\xE1s de \xE9l.*\r\n- CharacterID:
    Jared\r\n  LineID: L_dc490e2592df\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: Wait...
    this looks familiar. That\u2019s the ridge! That\u2019s the way back!\r\n   
    fr: Attends... \xE7a me dit quelque chose. C\u2019est la cr\xEAte ! C\u2019est
    le bon chemin!\r\n    es: Espera... esto me suena. \xA1Esa es la cresta! \xA1Ese
    es el camino de regreso!\r\n- CharacterID: Ava\r\n  LineID: L_2e2673368a71\r\n 
    LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: He really *is* guiding us...\r\n    fr: Il nous
    guide vraiment...\r\n    es: De verdad nos est\xE1 guiando...\r\n- CharacterID:
    Wolfstag\r\n  LineID: L_4c04459eaeba\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: *He pauses
    at the clearing's edge, makes eye contact, then silently disappears into the
    mist.*\r\n    fr: *Il s\u2019arr\xEAte \xE0 la lisi\xE8re de la clairi\xE8re,
    nous regarde, puis dispara\xEEt dans la brume.*\r\n    es: *Se detiene en el
    borde del claro, nos mira y desaparece entre la niebla.*\r\n- CharacterID: Jared\r\n 
    LineID: L_6e955da171a6\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: ...Goodbye, magic antler
    puppy. I hope you find your own trail home.\r\n    fr: ...Adieu, chien magique
    \xE0 bois. J\u2019esp\xE8re que tu retrouveras ton chemin.\r\n    es: ...Adi\xF3s,
    cachorro m\xE1gico de astas. Ojal\xE1 encuentres tu camino.\r\n- CharacterID:
    Ava\r\n  LineID: L_1d54676a6a5b\r\n  LocalizedDialogue:\r\n    en: ...Next time,
    I\u2019m bringing a map and a compass. And maybe pepper spray.\r\n    fr: ...La
    prochaine fois, je prends une carte, une boussole... et du spray au poivre.\r\n   
    es: ...La pr\xF3xima vez, llevar\xE9 un mapa, una br\xFAjula... y tal vez gas
    pimienta."
--- !u!114 &11400000
